---
// Guides.astro
---

<section id="guides" style="padding: 130px 0; background: var(--c-bg-alt); border-top: 1px solid var(--c-border);">
  <div style="max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 4vw;">
    <div class="mono" style="color: var(--c-gold); margin-bottom: 52px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;">
      / 06 GUIDES & TECHNICAL DOCS
      <span style="display: block; width: 80px; height: 1px; background: var(--c-border);"></span>
    </div>
    
    <div class="guide-grid gsap-stagger-container">
      <a class="guide gsap-stagger-item" href="#" style="opacity: 0;">
        <div class="guide-meta">
          <span style="color: var(--c-gold);">FMB</span>
          <span>5 MIN READ</span>
        </div>
        <h3>What is an FMB sketch, and why does the bank ask for it?</h3>
        <div class="read">READ DOC <span style="color: var(--c-gold); margin-left: 6px;">→</span></div>
      </a>
      
      <a class="guide gsap-stagger-item" href="#" style="opacity: 0;">
        <div class="guide-meta">
          <span style="color: var(--c-gold);">LAND SURVEY</span>
          <span>4 MIN READ</span>
        </div>
        <h3>Documents you need before a land survey in Tamil Nadu</h3>
        <div class="read">READ DOC <span style="color: var(--c-gold); margin-left: 6px;">→</span></div>
      </a>
      
      <a class="guide gsap-stagger-item" href="#" style="opacity: 0;">
        <div class="guide-meta">
          <span style="color: var(--c-gold);">PRICING</span>
          <span>6 MIN READ</span>
        </div>
        <h3>How much does a land survey cost in Chennai?</h3>
        <div class="read">READ DOC <span style="color: var(--c-gold); margin-left: 6px;">→</span></div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .guide-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .guide {
    border: 1px solid var(--c-border);
    background: var(--c-bg);
    padding: 32px;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    min-height: 260px;
    transition: transform 0.3s var(--ease), border-color 0.3s, background 0.3s;
  }
  .guide:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    border-color: var(--c-gold);
    background: #0D1624; /* slight hover highlight */
  }
  .guide-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    font-family: var(--f-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--c-t3);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .guide h3 {
    font-family: var(--f-body);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: var(--c-paper);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .read {
    margin-top: auto;
    font-family: var(--f-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--c-t2);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .guide:hover .read {
    color: var(--c-paper);
  }

  @media(max-width: 1024px) {
    .guide-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }
  @media(max-width: 768px) {
    .guide-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .guide { min-height: 200px; padding: 24px; }
  }
</style>
